	<section class="article-content clearfix">
		<p>I have written quite a few papers during my bachelors and masters. Some of them are:</p>
<p> </p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Bluetooth Technology</strong>
<ul>
<li>During my Bachelors in Computer Science at JNTU <span style="font-size: 12.16px;">(2002-200</span><span style="font-size: 12.16px;">6</span><span style="font-size: 12.16px;">)</span>, I wrote a paper and gave a presentation on the Bluetooth Wireless Technology when it was just a newly introduced technology.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Evolution of Gaming</strong>
<ul>
<li>During my bachelors in Computer Science at JNTU (2002-2006). I wrote a paper on the developing trend in gaming. I discussed how the games, controllers and the gaming hardware evolved from their ancestors to the present generation of gaming consoles. I chose this topic due to my interest in the trending technologies and Gaming.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><strong>Adaptive Web Interfaces</strong>
<ul>
<li>Because of my interest in Web Application Development, I chose the Technical Topic Paper on "<em>Adaptive Web Interfaces : A Study of how webpages adapt to a users interest</em>". And after researching and writing the paper I successfully presented the paper in front of the audience during my Masters in Computer Science at SIUe (2006-2009).</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p> </p> 	</section>
  
